Sentencas: The main emphasis of this work is to create a new perovskite material with three different compositions (La(0.75)Sr(0.25)Mn(0.5)Cr(0.5-)(x)AlxO(3), x = 0.1, 0.2, 0.3) applied in both Intermediate- and High-temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells (IT- and HT-SOFCs).
Titulo: Synthesis and electrochemical characterization of La0.75Sr0.25Mn0.5Cr0.5-xAlxO3, for IT- and HT-SOFCs

Sentencas: Perovskite-type polycrystalline La0.75Sr0.25Mn0.5Cr0.5-xAlxO3-delta (x = 0.1, 0.2, 0.3) powders were synthesized and formed in a single phase structure by a dry chemistry route (standard solid-state reaction method).
Titulo: Synthesis and electrochemical characterization of La0.75Sr0.25Mn0.5Cr0.5-xAlxO3, for IT- and HT-SOFCs

Sentencas: The effect of Al doping on physicochemical and surface properties has been discovered.
Titulo: Synthesis and electrochemical characterization of La0.75Sr0.25Mn0.5Cr0.5-xAlxO3, for IT- and HT-SOFCs

Sentencas: The compounds were crystallized in single phase rhombohedral symmetry (R-3C Space.
Titulo: Synthesis and electrochemical characterization of La0.75Sr0.25Mn0.5Cr0.5-xAlxO3, for IT- and HT-SOFCs
